이 곧 시작됩니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-58c7d446-fcca-433f-8d5d-0d8dc588e335\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-4c2e1a50-d6a1-439a-995a-b621c0e87d52\">시범사업이 잘 진행되면 첩약(한약) 건강보험 완전시행도 이어서 진행되리라 기대해 봅니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-843b00c9-55d6-4e8a-aa0a-5748a2411cec\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-01a98142-e701-41c6-a00c-0c667c4896eb\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-8a36c04c-8b69-4f42-9fe7-f3ae61942706\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-bb6640fb-95fc-4366-b09c-9ced5f4ab6e6\">첩약(한약) 건강보험 적용 시범사업에서는 3가지 질환</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-de64b151-9aeb-4c6f-b7b6-f1711dab7d38\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-f42bb81c-4f58-452f-b777-21777e8c4f69\">월경통(생리통)</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-4197112a-3d49-4e82-990d-5d6483d5ccd6\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-cdf7863d-f29f-4182-bd6f-3faf1e9c1fb4\">중풍후유증</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-a918c0a1-92e0-4855-ab8c-45fe8611caee\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-e601c06f-51e7-478a-a81b-accd59baaaae\">안면신경마비(구안와사)</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-a5a80e72-74f4-493d-bab5-59fe2697e719\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-6eaf0431-eef8-4fe5-b993-6ea959d68987\">에 대해</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style